| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1578 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 852b39e4-8d0b-54db-8cfa-b9ee5a31aeae"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
